column1: This collection contains various parts for constructing circuits composed of 4 plant transcription factors that are inducible with either doxycycline or beta-estradiol. Parts for modifying promoter strength are included. One fluorescent protein is avaiable, GFP. There are two sequence versions for the operators for each plant TF: 1)  sequences containing binding site sequences taken from the literature (lit based) and 2) sequences containing consensus binding site sequences taken from FootprintDB (footprintdb based).

column3: Seven binding sites for doxycycline sensing TF
Six inding sites for beta-estradiol sensing TF
beta-estradiol responsive DNA binding element (Z4 array with Estrogen receptor)

Sequence design is [[motif-1 30*N][motif-2 30*N]] * 1. Additional calculator settings: 40-60% GC content, reduce synthesis complexity, max. repeat size of 12.
